<h2>New Order Received</h2>

<p>Dear Admin,</p>

<p>A new order has been placed on the store.</p>

<p><strong>Order Reference:</strong> {{ order.reference }}<br>
<strong>Placed By:</strong> {{ order.user.email }}<br>
<strong>Date:</strong> {{ order.createdAt|date('F j, Y, H:i') }}</p>

<p><strong>Order Items:</strong></p>
{% for item in order.orderItems %}
    <p>
        • {{ item.productName }} — Quantity: {{ item.quantity }}, 
        Unit Price: ${{ item.price|number_format(2) }}, 
        Subtotal: ${{ (item.price * item.quantity)|number_format(2) }}
    </p>
    {% if not loop.last %}
        <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px dashed #ccc;">
    {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

<p><strong>Total:</strong> ${{ order.total|number_format(2) }}</p>

<p><strong>Shipping Address:</strong><br/>
    {{ order.shippingLine1 }}<br/>
    {% if order.shippingLine2 %}{{ order.shippingLine2 }}<br/>{% endif %}
    {{ order.shippingCity }}, {{ order.shippingCountry }} {{ order.shippingZipCode }}
</p>

<p>Please log in to the admin dashboard to view and process the order.</p>

<p>Regards,<br/>Your Store System</p>
